        "cooked": "<p>having a great lunch this friday, planning on opening up a monfortino-can\u2019t decide which vintage.  Choices: 00, 02, 04, 05, 06  It may come down to what I can put my hands on/which I have multiple of -but if anyone has a strong conviction.  Lunch will be around 1.30 so I\u2019m thinking double decant in the am.</p>\n<p>any opinions?</p>\n<p>thanks</p>\n<p>-paul</p>",
