      {
        "id": 2061176,
        "name": "Sarah Kirschbaum",
        "username": "Sarah_Kirschbaum",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/9d8465/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2016-11-21T16:59:19.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ol start=\"2000\">\n<li>See recent notes of mine and Kevin Shin.  Drinking beautifully and I, personally, would not decant it early in the AM.  I think it\u2019s still in the category of youthful that shows brilliantly out of the chute, then shuts down.  I fall into the category of decant the old ones, don\u2019t decant the young ones, though I understand not everyone agrees.</li>\n</ol>",
